categories: Category:Jedi trainees of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: The person lived during the time of the Galactic Republic and became a Padawan of Jedi Master Vandar Tokare.

The Padawan became one of Tokare's two Padawans, along with Derrica Praji. In 4225 BBY, Tokare, Praji and the other Padawan traveled to the planet Kaikielius, where they participated in the Kaikieli Reconquista, a campaign to retake the planet from criminals.
